"currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon></svg> <span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></span></a>不起作用，因为 <code>data:</code> 不是<a href="http://url.nodejs.cn/fbSryY" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">特殊协议<span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound"><path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h-32l0,0c-2.2,0-4,1.8-4,4v56C14.8,83.3,16.6,85.1,18.8,85.1z"></path> <polygon fill="currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon></svg> <span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></span></a>。 例如，尝试从 <code>data:text/javascript,import &quot;./foo&quot;;</code> 加载 <code>./foo</code> 无法解析，因为 <code>data:</code> URL 没有相对解析的概念。 正在使用的 <code>data:</code> URL 示例是：</p> <div class="language- line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-text"><code>import 'data:text/javascript,console.log(&quot;hello!&quot;);';
