console.log(M);
</code></pre> <div class="line-numbers-wrapper"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br></div></div><p>在以下条件下执行：</p> <div class="language- line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-text"><code>node --experimental-wasm-modules index.mjs
</code></pre> <div class="line-numbers-wrapper"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>将为 <code>module.wasm</code> 的实例化提供导出接口。</p> <h3 id="experimental-loaders"><a href="#experimental-loaders" class="header-anchor">#</a> Experimental loaders<a href="http://nodejs.cn/api-v12/esm.html#experimental-loaders" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#<span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound"><path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h-32l0,0c-2.2,0-4,1.8-4,4v56C14.8,83.3,16.6,85.1,18.8,85.1z"></path> <polygon fill="currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon></svg> <span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></span></a></h3> <p><a href="http://nodejs.cn/api-v12/esm/experimental_loaders.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">中英对照<span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="15" height="15" class="icon outbound"><path fill="currentColor" d="M18.8,85.1h56l0,0c2.2,0,4-1.8,4-4v-32h-8v28h-48v-48h28v-8h-32l0,0c-2.2,0-4,1.8-4,4v56C14.8,83.3,16.6,85.1,18.8,85.1z"></path> <polygon fill="currentColor" points="45.7,48.7 51.3,54.3 77.2,28.5 77.2,37.2 85.2,37.2 85.2,14.9 62.8,14.9 62.8,22.9 71.5,22.9"></polygon></svg> <span class="sr-only">(opens new window)</span></span></a></p> <p><strong>注意：此 API 目前正在重新设计，并将继续更改。</strong></p> <p>要自定义默认的模块解析，则可以选择通过 Node.js 的 <code>--experimental-loader ./loader-name.mjs</code> 参数提供加载器钩子。</p> <p>当使用钩子时，只适用于 ES 模块加载，而不适用于任何加载的 CommonJS 模块。</p> <h4 id="钩子"><a href="#钩子" class="header-anchor">#</a> 钩子<a href="http://nodejs.cn/api-v12/esm.html#hooks" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#<span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 1